ARTIST’S PROOF BY GABRIEL PICOLO NOW AVAILABLE FOR PURCHASE!

This is your opportunity to own a one of a kind, single-copy reproduction of Picolo’s published work including a hand-drawn sketch: you can choose the character you want!

Check the link in bio for all the art pieces available from TEEN TITANS: ROBIN and place your order!

#art #comicart #artistsproof #collectcomicart #picolo #robin #teentitans #chiarocurostudios

More and more comic book artists are making the switch to digital. What does this mean for the future of comic art collecting? Discover more about the single-copy, museum-quality ARTIST’S PROOFS from Chiaroscuro Studios!

#art #comicart #collectcomicart #artistsproof #chiaroscurostudios #comicscollection #marvelcomics #dccomics #imagecomics #boomstudios

We are proud to announce that Gabriel Picolo is now represented by Chiaroscuro Studios for art sales!

Gabriel Picolo is a brazilian comic artist and illustrator, mostly known worldwide due to his Teen Titans fanarts, which have yielded him the opportunity to work for DC on a series of Graphic Novels. He has also worked for clients worldwide as an illustrator and comic artist.

Picolo works exclusively on digital and his published art pieces on best selling graphic novels will be available for purchase as collectible single-copy Artist’s Proofs, which include a hand-drawn character pencilled by Picolo. That’s your chance to own a truly unique, signed art piece by your favorite artist!

The first art drop will be available on Saturday, January 20th. Stay tuned!

#art #collectcomicart #comicartfans #teentitans #gabrielpicolo #originart #comicart #comicartsales #comicartcollection #dccomics #robin #nightwing #chiaroscurostudios
